  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But Paul and I-- Paul had brought one piece of soap that we saved.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So we washed her feet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the everything worked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That child, we, later, had lots of contact with her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But, now, I forgot her name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Things go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But, so, this was not idyllic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But we were feeling comparatively safe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There came rumors that an American visa might come, you know, a special visa for people who are under special persecution.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] For that, you needed your own name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You couldn't go under the names that we were there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So, and for that, you needed a working [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That was amazing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We were born, again, by some way, getting our names back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no-- well, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is, meanwhile, the French, some people there that were in that village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Paul and I thought the best way would be to get married, because then we could get married together, to--",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
